snippet.title: Cookie Shop DS - UK Trailer (HQ)
snippet.description: Start a cookie shop, build it yourself and then set about making all sorts of great-tasting (or at least they look tasty) cookies and pastries for your customers. Meet your friends and then best them to become the No. 1 cookie shop in town. Mmm... cake!
